{"build_type":"library","description":"Walk a rename map object's members as a json-tree-node linked structure (node = first child, follow .next); each member's key field is the OLD package name and its text field is the NEW name. Call rename_one_package_by_name(old, new, roots) for each, in order. Tail-recurses over .next. The map is read from memory so renaming files on disk does not disturb iteration; each rename_one_package_by_name re-enumerates fresh. Safety invariant (enforced by the caller building the map): no NEW name equals any not-yet-processed OLD name, so renames never collide. Reuses rename_one_package_by_name.","module_name":"rename-packages-starting-dictionary-iteration","package_name":"rename-packages-starting-dictionary-iteration","function_definitions":{"rename-packages-starting-dictionary-iteration":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"child","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"roots","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"child"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"key","base":"child","dest":"old"},{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"text","base":"child","dest":"new"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"rename-single-package-through-identifier","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"old"},{"kind":"var","value":"new"},{"kind":"var","value":"roots"}],"result_assignment_variable":"rr","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"next","base":"child","dest":"nxt"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"rename-packages-starting-dictionary-iteration","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"nxt"},{"kind":"var","value":"roots"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}